==English==
===Proper noun===
'''[[Tajik]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Tajik Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for the [[Tajikistan|Republic of Tajikistan]] while under the rule of the [[Soviet Union]] (1924-1991).

